Node JS

•	Node JS is a server side JavaScript language.
•	Node JS runs on modified V8 Engine.
•	It does not have windows and document Object.
•	It was created by  Ryan Dahl, by modifying the v8 engine.

Browser JS

•	Browser JS is a client side JavaScript language.
•	Browser JS runs on the actual V8 Engine.
•	Browser JS have windows and document Object.
•	It was found by Brendan Eich, for Netscape.
